## Description
The **Update Asset **task allows to create a new release and deploy of an [Asset](/doxee-platform/docs/asset-resource-reference) through a Batch Production job.

## Configuration
**![](data:image/png;base64,)**

- In the **Alias **field, enter the name of the task that will be displayed in the workflow.

- Click on the **Asset &gt; Resource **field and select the [Asset](/doxee-platform/docs/asset-resource-reference) resource to use.

> Important

The Asset resource must already exist and have been released and deployed manually at least once. Otherwise, it won't be available for selection.

## Use within a workflow
The Update Asset task should be used as the last task in the workflow. It may also be the only task in a workflow.

## Input
The task consumes the output of a previous task as long as it contains a supported file format, for example a Data Transformation catalog.

## Output
The task will create a new release of the selected Asset resource and deploy it to the same tenant with the automatic release description "**Automatic release from Batch Job {{jobnumber}}**".
